# Cluster Management Directory
#
# Each subdirectory is a real cluster (e.g. clusters/justin/) with its own
# .env, optional nginx/cloudflared config, and data/. Only `template/` —
# the source of `task cluster:new` — is tracked.

*
!.gitignore
!template/
!template/**

# Inside template/, never track real credentials even if a user drops them
# in by mistake.
template/cloudflared/credentials.json
